profile:
CSJ Developments Ltd. is a leading General Contracting, Construction Management, and Design/Build development company serving Alberta and Western Canada.

We support our clients from an initial concept at the early design stage, through pre-construction and bid phases, the construction phase and to final close-out.

To date we have built, renovated and remodelled more than 250,000 square feet of space for both residential and commercial clients.

Some of our specialties include but are not restricted to custom homes, carriage homes and laneway houses, secondary suites, and condo developments.
